          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4465736372697074696f6e23232344415441232323">Models equipped with wings move in the same way as Jump Infantry. In addition, models that have wings can be kept in reserve and arrive using the Deep Strike rules.</characteristic>
