      <rules>
        <rule name="Repair" id="7942-4136-ecdb-f430" hidden="false">
          <description>If a Chaos Rhino is immobilised, the crew may attempt a repair in their Shooting phase (this prevents the vehicle from shooting). To do so, roll a D6 - on a 6 the Immobilised result is repaired and the Chaos Rhino is free to move again in later turns.</description>
