                <rule name="Obliterator Weapons" id="af33-af7b-c4a0-9fcf" hidden="false">
                  <description>Obliterators may fire one wepaon from those available in each Shooting phase, and the entire squad must choose the same weapon. The weapons available are: lascannon, multi-melta, plasma cannon, twin-linked plasma gun, twin-linked meltagun, twin-linked flamer.</description>
                </rule>
