      </infoLinks>
      <rules>
        <rule name="The Betrayer" id="56fb-1d84-0bcd-6612" hidden="false">
          <description>Any of Khârn&apos;s to hit rolls of 1 in close combat have hit his own side. Resolve the hits on a random friendly unit engaged in the same combat, as if they were hit by the enemy, using Khârn&apos;s weapons and profile. If there are no other units in the same combat as Khârn, these attacks simply miss.</description>
        </rule>
        <rule name="Blessing of the Blood God" id="9322-6e8f-6ae5-b9f5" hidden="false">
          <description>Khârn is immune to the effects of psychic powers, and force weapons count as normal power weapons against him.</description>
        </rule>
      </rules>
