      </entryLinks>
      <rules>
        <rule name="Enhanced Warriors" id="4c93-17f1-336d-1267" hidden="false">
          <description>For +3 points per model, any number of Chaos Space Marine squads can be &apos;enhanced&apos; by Bile&apos;s treatment. At the start of the battle, after both sides have set up but before the first turn, roll a D6 for each enhanced squad and consult the table below.

D1 - Berserk Rage!: Make an armour save for each warrior, removing any who fail. Survivors are Fearless and at +1 Strength for the remainder of the game.
D2-5 - Stable: The enhanced warriors are Fearless and have +1 Strength for the entire game.
D6 - Created a Monster: The warriors are Fearless and add +2 to their Strength for the entire game. At the end of every owning player&apos;s turn, one of the squads members is removed as a casualty (owner&apos;s choice).</description>
        </rule>
      </rules>
